  &lt;p id="P37snh"&gt;Conventional wisdom says that if you want the very lowest prices on a 4K TV you wait until Black Friday / Cyber Monday in November, but &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/24191617/amazon-prime-day-tech-deals-guide-2024"&gt;Amazon’s Prime Day&lt;/a&gt; can offer some solid discounts during the dog days of summer. &lt;/p&gt;
