      &lt;img alt="An aerial view shows the rooftops of homes and buildings in a flooded area." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/scVMmS0rUxQo-mQDZQNmPp4hGf8=/0x0:4896x3264/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73464130/934626432.0.jpg" /&gt;
